snippet.title: Version 1.5 Trailer - "The Crepuscule Zone" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
Greet an envoy of wraiths and guests of a stranger nature... While sailing across a firmament enshadowed by night, the unseen and eerie will descend between lapses of expectation.

English Voice:
Argenti — Adam Michael Gold
March 7th — Skyler Davenport
Guinaifen — Morgan Lauré
Sushang — Anjali Kunapaneni
Huohuo — Courtney Lin
Possessed Spiritfarer — Analesa Fisher
